---
const data = [
  {
    category: "Innovative Design",
    text: "Our cutting-edge design offers a fresh, modern look that transforms your project into a standout experience. ",
    items: ["Revolutionizing communication", "Enhancing productivity"],
  },
  {
    category: "Powerful Functionality",
    text: "Equipped with advanced features and tools, our solution effortlessly manages complex tasks and workflows. ",
    items: ["Unlocking innovative solutions", "Enabling interoperability"],
  },
];
---

<section>
  <div class="px-8 py-32 mx-auto md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-7xl relative">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <span
        class="font-mono text-xs font-medium tracking-tight text-blue-600 uppercase"
        >Your tagline</span
      >
      <h1
        class="text-4xl mt-4 font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 lg:text-balance">
        Transform your visitors into users with an engaging headline
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-base font-medium text-gray-500 lg:text-pretty">
        The fastest method for working together on staging and temporary
        environments.
      </p>
    </div>
    <dl
      class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-12 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-16 mt-12">
      <div>
        <div class="text-blue-500 flex gap-3 items-center">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-filters"
            ><path
              stroke="none"
              d="M0 0h24v24H0z"
              fill="none"
            ></path><path d="M12 8m-5 0a5 5 0 1 0 10 0a5 5 0 1 0 -10 0"
            ></path><path d="M8 11a5 5 0 1 0 3.998 1.997"></path><path
              d="M12.002 19.003a5 5 0 1 0 3.998 -8.003"></path></svg
          >
          <dt class="tracking-tight text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">
            Innovative Design
          </dt>
        </div>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 text-pretty">
          Our cutting-edge design offers a fresh, modern look that transforms
          your project into a standout experience.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-blue-500 flex gap-3 items-center">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-wave-square"
            ><path
              stroke="none"
              d="M0 0h24v24H0z"
              fill="none"
            ></path><path d="M3 12h5v8h4v-16h4v8h5"></path></svg
          >
          <dt class="tracking-tight text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">
            Powerful Functionality
          </dt>
        </div>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 text-pretty">
          Equipped with advanced features and tools, our solution effortlessly
          manages complex tasks and workflows.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-blue-500 flex gap-3 items-center">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-arrow-iteration"
            ><path
              stroke="none"
              d="M0 0h24v24H0z"
              fill="none"
            ></path><path d="M8.5 16a5.5 5.5 0 1 0 -5.5 -5.5v.5"></path><path
              d="M3 16h18"></path><path d="M18 13l3 3l-3 3"></path></svg
          >
          <dt class="tracking-tight text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">
            Easy Integration
          </dt>
        </div>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 text-pretty">
          Integrating with existing systems is smooth and hassle-free, thanks to
          our incredible flexible approach.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
    <dl
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-12 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-16 mt-12 lg:mt-24">
      <div
        class="p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl flex flex-col h-full justify-between">
        <div>
          <span
            class="font-mono text-xs font-medium tracking-tight text-blue-600 uppercase"
            >Your tagline</span
          >
          <h1 class="text-4xl mt-4 font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
            Let's get it done together, whenerever, forever.
          </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-12">
          <button
            class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 hover:to-indigo-800 shadow focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-950 focus:ring-offset-2 ring-offset-gray-200 hover:shadow-none"
            aria-label="Action">
            Get started
          </button>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 md:text-left">
            <span class="block">This is some support text</span>
            <span class="block">and this is also.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        x-data="{ open: false }"
        class="block w-full mt-12 lg:mt-0 relative">
        <img
          alt="#_"
          class="relative  drop-shadow h-full object-cover w-full"
          src="/images/whiteCard.svg"
        />
        <div class="absolute bg-gray-900/50 inset-0 rounded-3xl"></div>
        <button
          class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex items-center justify-center size-12 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 hover:to-indigo-800 shadow focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-950 focus:ring-offset-2 ring-offset-gray-200 hover:shadow-none"
          @click="open = true">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-player-play"
            ><path
              stroke="none"
              d="M0 0h24v24H0z"
              fill="none"
            ></path><path d="M7 4v16l13 -8z"></path></svg
          >
        </button>

        <!-- Modal -->
        <div
          class="fixed inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-200/70"
          x-show="open"
          @keydown.escape.window="open = false"
          aria-labelledby="modal-title"
          role="dialog"
          aria-modal="true"
          x-cloak>
          <div
            class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow transform transition-all max-w-3xl w-full"
            @click.away="open = false">
            <div
              class="border-b bg-gray-50 px-4 py-3 sm:px-6 flex justify-between items-center">
              <h2
                class="font-medium text-gray-900"
                id="modal-title">
                Watch Video
              </h2>
              <button
                @click="open = false"
                class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"
                aria-label="Close modal">
                <span class="sr-only">Close</span>
                <svg
                  class="size-4"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor">
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2">
              <iframe
                class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-2xl h-96"
                width="100%"
                height="100%"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID"
                frameborder="0"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
